# Security Audits & Risk Management 🛡️

Welcome to the Security Audits section of my portfolio. 

This folder contains projects, reports, and documentation related to the strategic side of cybersecurity. The activities housed here demonstrate my ability to analyze organizational vulnerabilities and propose effective hardening measures.

### Core Focus Areas:
* Vulnerability Assessments
* Risk Management & Mitigation Strategies
* Network Hardening (Firewalls, Ports, IAM)
* Security Policy Documentation

Each subfolder within this directory represents a specific scenario or case study where I applied security principles to protect corporate assets and prevent data breaches.
